<section class="hero"><div class="hero-inner"><div class="breadcrumb"><a href="index.html">SFGS</a> <span>/</span> Admission <span>/</span> Fee Payment</div><h2>Fee <em>Payment</em></h2><div class="hero-divider"></div><p class="hero-tagline">Transparent fee structure with flexible payment options designed to support every SFGS family.</p></div></section>
<div class="motto-strip"><span class="star">★</span><p>Affordable · Flexible · Transparent</p><span class="star">★</span></div>
<div class="main-wrap"><main class="content">
<div class="fee-intro-card">
  <h3>Transparent. Predictable. Manageable.</h3>
  <p>The school's fee structure is comprehensive and covers all expenses for students across all classes. We are committed to providing clarity and flexibility so that no qualified student misses out on a quality education.</p>
</div>

<h2 class="section-heading">Fee Categories</h2>

<div class="fee-categories">
  <div class="fee-cat-card">
    <div class="fee-cat-icon">🎯</div>
    <h3>Admission Fee</h3>
    <p>A one-time, non-refundable fee charged to new students joining SFGS. Covers registration, induction materials, and initial onboarding.</p>
    <div class="fee-tag">New Students Only</div>
  </div>
  <div class="fee-cat-card">
    <div class="fee-cat-icon">📚</div>
    <h3>Tuition Fees</h3>
    <p>Covers academic instruction, learning materials, examinations, and access to the library and laboratories. Tuition varies depending on the class level.</p>
    <div class="fee-tag">Billed Termly</div>
  </div>
  <div class="fee-cat-card">
    <div class="fee-cat-icon">🏠</div>
    <h3>Boarding Fees</h3>
    <p>Covers accommodation in our well-maintained dormitories along with three nutritious meals per day. Boarding fees vary by class level.</p>
    <div class="fee-tag">Termly Boarders</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="payment-methods">
  <h3>💳 Approved Payment Methods</h3>
  <div class="methods-grid">
    <div class="method-card"><div class="method-icon">🏦</div><div><h4>Bank Deposit</h4><p>Direct deposit to the school's official bank account using the parent's bank slip.</p><span class="method-detail">Account details provided with admission letter</span></div></div>
    <div class="method-card"><div class="method-icon">📱</div><div><h4>M-Pesa Paybill</h4><p>Convenient mobile money transfer using the school's official Paybill number.</p><span class="method-detail">Paybill: See admission documents</span></div></div>
    <div class="method-card"><div class="method-icon">💻</div><div><h4>Electronic Transfer</h4><p>Online bank-to-bank transfer (EFT/RTGS) for institutional and corporate payments.</p><span class="method-detail">SWIFT details available on request</span></div></div>
    <div class="method-card"><div class="method-icon">🏢</div><div><h4>Bankers' Cheque</h4><p>Payment by bankers' cheque addressed to St Francis Girls Suwerwa.</p><span class="method-detail">Submit to the school finance office</span></div></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="flex-plan">
  <h3>🤝 Our Flexible Fee Plan</h3>
  <p>The management of St Francis Girls Suwerwa operates a comprehensive fee payment plan that enables parents and guardians to fund the school fees comfortably — without undue strain or disruption to learning. Students' education continuity is our priority.</p>
  <div class="flex-features">
    <div class="flex-feature">Termly instalment options</div>
    <div class="flex-feature">Multiple payment channels</div>
    <div class="flex-feature">Transparent fee breakdown</div>
    <div class="flex-feature">Receipt for every payment</div>
    <div class="flex-feature">Continuity-first approach</div>
    <div class="flex-feature">Confidential consultation</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="policy-note">
  📝 <strong>Important:</strong> Detailed fee structures, exact amounts, and bank account details are provided to admitted students via the official admission letter and fee structure document. For the most current information, please contact the <strong>School Finance Office</strong> directly via the contact details on this page.
</div>

